com.team1389.util

Class ButtonEnumMap<E extends java.lang.Enum>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.team1389.util.ButtonEnumMap<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - the enum type

    public class ButtonEnumMap<E extends java.lang.Enum>
extends java.lang.Object
    Maps a set of boolean streams to the values of an enum

    When any of the streams returns true, the value is set to the mapping of that stream

    This class works best with latched streams.

    Author:
    amind
    See Also:
    Latching an input stream
